title: HOUR 3- Rob Manfred Oct 23, 2020

description:
MLB Commissioner Rob Manfred tells Dan that he would really like to expand the playoffs. The Commissioner tells Dan that he is glad that the league was able to settle and achieve the 60 regular season games.
